BLUE RIDGE NATURAL GAS & OIL CORPORATION v. D. E. DUNNE, Jr., et al. No. 5667. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Oct. 8, 1957. Hershenstein & Edwards, New York City, for appellant. McKay & McKay, El Dorado, Kan., for appellees.

Before BRATTON, Chief Judge, and HUXMAN, Circuit Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Dismissed on application of appellant.
